comment_data.body:
Just to be extra safe/explicit, set `pending_default_colors` first?

```suggestion
    pending_default_colors = false;
    ui_call_default_colors_set(normal_fg, normal_bg, normal_sp,
                               cterm_normal_fg_color, cterm_normal_bg_color);
```

